data.title: Segmentation Fault while optimising model · Issue #426 · stereolabs/zed-sdk
data.meta_description: Hi I am encountering a segmentation fault in ZED_Object_detection_birds_eye_viewer when the model is being optimised for my PC. My PC's configuration is Ryzen 9, RTX3070, Ubuntu 20.04, Nvidia driver 470, CUDA 11.0, ZED SDK 3.5.3. I have ...
